      <title>诺华斥资 27 亿欧元收购 MorphoSys 以获得抗癌药物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/morphosys-surges-on-report-novartis-is-in-talks-to-buy-drugmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺华公司同意以 27 亿欧元（合 29 亿美元）收购 MorphoSys AG，​​将这家德国制药商的癌症治疗药物纳入其产品线中，这家瑞士制药公司一直在努力加强该产品线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/morphosys-surges-on-report-novartis-is-in-talks-to-buy-drugmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:47:08 GMT</pubDate>
